com.opengamma.strata.calc.runner

Class CalculationTaskCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opengamma.strata.calc.runner.CalculationTaskCell
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Bean, ImmutableBean

    public final class CalculationTaskCell
extends Object
implements ImmutableBean
    A single cell within a calculation task.

    Each CalculationTask calculates a result for one or more cells. This class capture details of each cell.
